<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Student Feedback</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Ubuntu+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400;1,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-sRIl4kxILFvY47J16cr9ZwB07vP4J8+LH7qKQnuqkuIAvNWLzeN8tE5YBujZqJLB" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link href="feedback-styles.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body class="m-3">

    <div class="bg-dark-subtle m-1 mb-3 p-4 rounded-4 text-center">
        <h1>We value your feedback</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Instructions</h2>
            <p>As one of our students, your thoughts, feedback and comments are import to us.</p>
            <p>Please send them using this form.</p>
            <p>If you would like us to fllow up with you, include your contact information.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <form action="/submit-feedback">
                <label class="form-label m-2" for="name">Name</label>
                <input class="form-control m-2" id="name" name="name">

                <br>

                <label class="form-label m-2" for="email">Email</label>
                <input class="form-control m-2" type="email" name="email" id="email">

                <br>
                <label class="form-label m-2" for="comments">Comments</label> 
                <textarea class="form-control m-2" rows="10" cols="45" name="comments" id="comments" required></textarea>

                <br>
                <p class="mx-2">Are you a current student?</p>

                <div class="form-check">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="yes" name="current-students" id="yes">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="yes">Yes</label>
                </div>

                <div class="form-check">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" value="no" name="current-students" id="no">
                    <label class="form-check-label" for="no">No</label>
                </div>

                <br>

                <input class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">

            </form>
        </div> <!-- end of second form col div-->
    </div> <!-- end of second form row div-->
</body>
</html>